<div id="main-container" class="container-fluid">
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Track your job search</h1>
      <p>Job hunting is hard. Monitoring your job hunting progress shouldn't be. Coffee Date is here to help.</p>
      <br><br>

      <a class="btn btn-success btn-lg" id="signupbutton" role="button">Sign Up</a>
      <a class="btn btn-success btn-lg" role="button" id="signinbutton">Login</a>

      <div id="signup">
      <%= render partial: "welcome/signup"%>
      </div>
      <div id='signin'>
        <%= render partial: 'welcome/signin'%>
      </div>

  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-3"></div>
    <div class="col-xs-2">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></span>
      <h4>Monitor your recent and upcoming activities.</h4>
      <br>
      <p> Forget about forgetting about upcoming interviews, follow up notes, and phone calls.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-2">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span>
      <h4>Store notes about advocates</h4>
      <br>
      <p>Store details about the people who are helping you get jobs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-2">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-inbox"></span>
      <h4>Gather all your info in one place</h4>
      <br>
      <p>Never forget who is the CTO of that one company or which is their blog. Keep all of your contact emails and phone numbers in one place.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-3"></div>
  </div>


</div>
